name: SP11/SP1/3 | Verify user cannot activate Trial period with incomplete card number
description: Verify user cannot activate Trial period with invalid card number
descriptionHtml: Verify user cannot activate Trial period with invalid card number

testStage.description: Verify user cannot activate Trial period with invalid card number

steps.name: Preconditions: SignUp Trial user without payment
Navigate to Trial user registration page.
Verify user is on Confirm account page.
Retrieve the confirmation link from the user's email.
Wait for toast to be hidden
Fill in the "Full Name On Card" input field
Fill in the "Card Number" input field
Fill in the "Expiration Date" input field
Click on 'Start My 7-Day Free Trial' button.
Verify toast with Error message Your card number is incomplete.
Verify card number has warning red color

labels.name: titlePath
labels.value: > chromium > registration.spec.js > Negative tests for Trial user Registration
